            <h1 class="webcast-title">ISSA International Series: Threat Detection - Trends and Technology</h1>
                        <div ng-cloak class="webcast-description-wrapper" ng-class="{'webcast-description-collapsed': !webcast.description.expanded && '1'}">
                <div>
                    <span class="webcast-description">The world is changing, attacks come at the speed of light, and are changing so fast detection is almost impossible.  So, how do we tell when we are being attacked?  What new technologies are coming down the pipe?  This session will cover these and many more topics.<br />
