                                            <meta itemprop="image" content="/communication/337605/thumbnail_1540568817.png">
                                        <meta itemprop="description" content="Encryption has long been used to help secure corporate data at the endpoint, to protect company information from unauthorized access by would-be bad actors. As more and more corporations are moving data and solutions to the cloud as a way of reducing costs, there are often questions about how encryption and digital forensics might work in a virtual environment.  During this webinar, weâll discuss the role of encryption in forensics, and how it can be adopted in cloud-based solutions, as well to ensure data security as your data moves. no matter where your data resides.">

