            <h1 class="webcast-title">ISSA Thought Leadership Series: Security Event Overload-How to Net it Out</h1>
                        <div ng-cloak class="webcast-description-wrapper" ng-class="{'webcast-description-collapsed': !webcast.description.expanded && '1'}">
                <div>
                    <span class="webcast-description">How do you manage the thousands or tens of thousands of security alerts that are generated by your systems each day? Hear about strategies from practitioners who are dealing with âevent overloadâ and then listen to a follow-up with a discussion about how security products that are building actionable information into their reporting in order to ease the burden.<br />
<br />
Moderator: Steve Tcherchian, CISO and Director of Product Management, XYPRO Technology<br />
<br />
Speakers:<br />
Robert Hamilton, Director, Product Marketing, Imperva <br />
Shelly Herschkovitz, Product Manager, Research &amp; Innovation, Imperva<br />
Scott McCoy, IT Director, Medtronic<br />
Jessica Doyle, Director of Threat Assessment for Optiv</span>
                </div>
            </div>

                            <div class="webcast-description-toggle-button-wrapper">
                    <button ng-if="!webcast.description.expanded"  class="webcast-description-toggle-button" ng-click="toggleDescription()">...more</button>
                    <button ng-if="webcast.description.expanded" class="webcast-description-toggle-button" ng-click="toggleDescription()">...less</button>
                </div>
            
                                        
            
    
    
