                <span class="title">Practical Advice for the Proactive SOC: How to Escape The Vicious Cycle of React</span>

                    

    <span class="startDate upcomingDate" title="Start date">
        <span class="BTDate date" data-timestamp="1555520400" data-format="M j Y">Apr 17 2019</span>
        <span class="BTDate time" data-timestamp="1555520400" data-format="g:i a">5:00 pm</span>
        <span class="jsTimezoneClock timezone-clock usersTimezone">UTC</span>
    </span>


