            <a class="add-to-calendar-widget-google-calendar-link" href="https://www.google.com/calendar/render?action=TEMPLATE&amp;pli=1&amp;sf=true&amp;output=xml&amp;text=ISSA%20Thought%20Leadership%20Series%3A%20Cybersecurity%20risk%20is%20a%20shared%20responsibility&amp;details=Click%20here%20to%20attend%3A%20http%3A%2F%2Fwww.brighttalk.com%2Fwebcast%2F16125%2F335084%3Futm_campaign%3Dgoogle-calendar%26utm_source%3Dbrighttalk-portal%26utm_medium%3Dcalendar%0A%0AAs%20organizations%20increase%20the%20quantity%20and%20complexity%20of%20digital%20services%20they%20provide%20to%20their%20customers%20they%20are%20increasingly%20relying%20on%20partners%2C%20vendors%20and%203rd%20parties%20to%20support%20them.%0A%0AThis%20means%20that%20the%20old%20model%20of%20snapshot%20assessments%20is%20falling%20behind%20in%20providing%20the%20timely%20conversations%20needed%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20dynamic%20environment%20where%20data%20sharing%20is%20assumed%20and%20partners%20are%20providing%20business%20critical%20services%20outside%20an%20organization%E2%80%99s%20infrastructure.%0A%0AJoin%20us%20to%20discuss%20how%20digital%20attack%20surfaces%20are%20expanding%2C%20what%20information%20is%20available%20to%20assess%20risk%2C%20the%20methodology%20on%20what%20makes%20up%20a%20score%20and%20where%20to%20use%20them%2C%20how%20to%20engage%20in%20constructive%20conversations%20with%20your%20partners%20and%20showcase%20results%20to%20leadership.%0A%0AModerator%3A%0AKen%20Dunham%0A%0ASpeakers%3A%0AVamsi%20Gullapalli%2C%20Product%20Team%2C%20RiskIQ%0ASteve%20Tcherchian%2C%20CISO%2C%20XYPRO%20Technology%20Corporation%0AWayne%20Proctor%2C%20Vice%20President%2C%20Information%20Security%2C%20WestRock&amp;location=BrightTALK&amp;dates=20180912T170000Z%2F20180912T180200Z" ga-click-tracker ga-click-tracker-action="Add to calendar" ga-click-tracker-category="Onboarding flow" ga-click-tracker-label="Google calendar" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-google"></i> Google</a>
